room_title: Escape room "The Wall" by Enigma Escape Rooms in Buffalo
room_description: You're a CIA Operative in East Berlin during the height of the Cold War, on the hunt for a missing Spy. It's a race against time to find your missing colleague, help them complete their mission and prevent the start of World War III while evading capture by the omnipresent East German Stasi. Can you save the world?
